young and pretty, Lady Xiang.

138
00:09:48,724 --> 00:09:50,004
Thank you, General Fu.

139
00:09:50,563 --> 00:09:52,003
Thank you, Lady Rong Le.

140
00:09:52,263 --> 00:09:53,743
