to make such high quality dress.

151
00:10:22,174 --> 00:10:23,894
It suits your elegance, Lady Rong Le.

152
00:10:24,060 --> 00:10:25,340
Zhao Yun.

153
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:27,820
