182
00:11:46,172 --> 00:11:49,648
The banquet is going to start now.
Let's take our seats.

183
00:11:52,038 --> 00:11:53,398
Thank you, Your Highness.

184
00:11:57,531 --> 00:11:58,651
Come.

185
00:11:59,105 --> 00:12:00,705
I'm very happy today that...

186
00:12:01,060 --> 00:12:04,877
