banquet of my beloved Lady Xiang.

187
00:12:05,370 --> 00:12:09,195
I wish for her to be
young and happy always.

188
00:12:09,388 --> 00:12:11,585
Come, let's cheers.

189
00:12:16,220 --> 00:12:17,540
